\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/visions-of-mana-steam-deck-performance-settings-1851636872\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/visions-of-mana-steam-deck-performance-settings-1851636872\"\u003ehave struggled on the Steam Deck\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e. So you can probably understand that my expectations for \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/final-fantasy-7-rebirth-review-ps5-1851276129\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/final-fantasy-7-rebirth-review-ps5-1851276129\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eFinal Fantasy VII Rebirth\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cem\u003e \u003c/em\u003ewere pretty low. If Cloud’s adventure ran well enough that I could sneak in some games of Queen’s Blood on the go, I’d consider it a win. - Timothy Monbleau \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/ff7-rebirth-best-steam-deck-graphics-settings-1851754163\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/ff7-rebirth-best-steam-deck-graphics-settings-1851754163\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"2c5b806f86f30d8d835055c133fac8b2\" data-recommend-id=\"image://2c5b806f86f30d8d835055c133fac8b2\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Donkey Kong and a smaller monkey race forward while a blurred image of gameplay decorates the background.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"Donkey Kong and a smaller monkey race forward while a blurred image of gameplay decorates the background.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationright