o meaningful changes to the gameplay added in this version.  - Billy Givens \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/donkey-kong-country-returns-hd-switch-how-long-1851754095\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/donkey-kong-country-returns-hd-switch-how-long-1851754095\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"f4016b6a177d201de48a59cfa07b8553\" data-recommend-id=\"image://f4016b6a177d201de48a59cfa07b8553\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A promotional screenshot of Path of Exile 2. The Monk character is attacking several monsters with a staff while a large bipedal creature prepares to swing its club.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"A promotional screenshot of Path of Exile 2. The Monk character is attacking several monsters with a staff while a large bipedal creature prepares to swing its club.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"false\" data-imagerights=\"other-license\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/f4016b6a177d201de48a59cfa07b8553.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/f4016b6a177d201de48a59cfa07b8553.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/f4016b6a177d201de48a59cfa07b8553.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"A promotional screenshot of Path of Exile 2. The Monk character is attacking several monsters with a staff while a large bipedal creature prepares to swing its club.\" data-chomp-id=\"f4016b6a177d201de48a59cfa07b8553\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"A promotional screenshot of Path of Exile 2. The Monk character is attacking several monsters with a staff while a large bipedal creature prepares to swing its club.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/f4016b6a177d201de48a59cfa07b8553.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage: Grinding Gear Games\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"f4016b6a177d201de48a59cfa07b8553\" data-recommend-id=\"image://f4016b6a177d201de48a59cfa07b8553\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A promotional screenshot of Path of Exile 2. The Monk character is attacking several monsters with a staff while a large bipedal creature prepares to swing its club.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eARPGs like \u003cem\u003ePath of Exile 2\u003c/em\u003e and portable gaming devices like the Steam Deck go together like spaghetti and meatballs. Fighting huge mobs of enemies and grinding out rare loot is perfect for pick-up-and-play gaming, especially while you lay in bed listening to all those podcasts your friends keep bugging you to check out. Granted, this is only a great experience if the game you’re playing runs well on Valve’s flagship portable device, so how does \u003cem\u003ePath of Exile 2\u003c/em\u003e hold up? - Timothy Monbleau \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/path-of-exile-2-steam-deck-graphics-settings-diablo-1851754197\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/path-of-exile-2-steam-deck-graphics-settings-diablo-1851754197\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"791602b12f5168c3c92b5d69b6d0b78c\" data-recommend-id=\"image://791602b12f5168c3c92b5d69b6d0b78c\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Captain America stands with his shield against a fantasy background with a large building.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"Captain America stands with his shield against a fantasy background with a large building.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/791602b12f5168c3c92b5d69b6d0b78c.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/791602b12f5168c3c92b5d69b6d0b78c.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/791602b12f5168c3c92b5d69b6d0b78c.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Captain America stands with his shield against a fantasy background with a large building.\" data-chomp-id=\"791602b12f5168c3c92b5d69b6d0b78c\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"Captain America stands with his shield against a fantasy background with a large building.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/791602b12f5168c3c92b5d69b6d0b78c.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Marvel Games / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"791602b12f5168c3c92b5d69b6d0b78c\" data-recommend-id=\"image://791602b12f5168c3c92b5d69b6d0b78c\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Captain America stands with his shield against a fantasy background with a large building.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt is only fitting that the First Avenger himself, Captain America, was one of the first heroes to join \u003cem\u003eMarvel Rivals\u003c/em\u003e. For a character whose primary weapon is a shield, it makes sense that Cap would take on \u003cem\u003eRivals’\u003c/em\u003e version of the Tank role as a Vanguard. However, unlike beefier Tanks, the Sentinel of Liberty requires a little more finesse than other characters like Hulk.  - Simon Estey \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/marvel-rivals-how-to-play-captain-america-tank-1851754920\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/marvel-rivals-how-to-play-captain-america-tank-1851754920\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"1bf1a93992c98830574afb53b3c9d7b3\" data-recommend-id=\"image://1bf1a93992c98830574afb53b3c9d7b3\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Mr. Fantastic stands in a hangar.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"Mr. Fantastic stands in a hangar.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/